description: Extensions and alterations to the building including demolition and replacement of the top three levels with remodelled and extended three floors plus new rooftop plant floor and additional basement excavation, to provide retail (Class A1) floorspace at basement, ground and first floor levels with 89 residential flats (Class C3) on the floors above; car/cycle parking facilities, servicing area, storage, plant and landscaping; associated external alterations.
